    <p>{`A naive approach to ERC20 token lists is automatically displaying every asset. While this is maximally decentralized, it opens up the door for phishing, scams, and presents users with way too many options.`}</p>
    <p>{`Another naive approach is creating a decentralized governance system as a gatekeeper, with the hope that this governance system will be fairer than the gatekeepers that came before it.`}</p>
    <p>{`Most projects opt for the easiest and most practical solution: maintaining a list supported by their own reputation. `}</p>
